docs.text: Welcome to My Project Documentation This documentation contains components written in multiple languages: C++ Module Documentation Java GUI Documentation Python Backend Documentation About the Project This software simulates high-harmonic generation using numerical methods. It consists of: - a C++ core simulation engine, - a Java-based GUI frontend, - and a Python integration/management layer. Use the sidebar or the links above to navigate.
